Package: togolab
Title: Shared Utilities for the Bjornstad-Pyle (BPT) Lab
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ye Ji", "Choi", email = "yejichoi@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("BPT Lab", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Lab-wide helper functions for the Bjornstad-Pyle Translational
    research group. Resolves per-user file system paths from an external
    configuration file, configures access to the lab S3 (Kopah) store, loads
    and collapses the harmonized dataset, and bundles miscellaneous utilities
    the lab uses across projects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
